man(25.10)                                                          man(25.10)

Name man
Syntax
Parameter  <command_name> Indicates the name of the text command (or variable)
       for which the manual information is required. <msg_id> Specifies a mes-
       sage ID in the format like ABC-123. The output will show the  log  file
       message  and  any  extended  help  description  that can include likely
       causes, possible fixes, and possible workarounds for this msg_id.
Example
                           Fri Apr 04 01:25:37 2025                 man(25.10)